[Dictionary Stories](http://www.dictionarystories.com) A neat project from Jez Burrows, one of the few designers at Facebook who actually work with analog materials, and the publisher and designer of a fantastic short story collection. He&rsquo;s writing short stories &ldquo;composed entirely of example sentences from the New Oxford American Dictionary.&rdquo;
